    <!-- Card 3: Reinforcement Learning -->
    <div class="concept-card fade-in">
      <div class="concept-icon">🎮</div>
      <h3>Reinforcement Learning</h3>
      <p>An agent learns by interacting with an environment — taking actions, receiving rewards or penalties, and updating its policy. No labeled data; learning emerges from trial and error over thousands of episodes.</p>
      <div class="concept-diagram">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 340 160" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" style="background:rgba(0,0,0,0.3);border-radius:8px;">
