          <text x="306" y="78" text-anchor="middle" fill="#52b788" font-size="8" font-weight="bold">MODEL</text>
          <text x="306" y="91" text-anchor="middle" fill="#74c69d" font-size="7">🧠 fit</text>
          <!-- Bottom label -->
          <text x="170" y="148" text-anchor="middle" fill="#7a9e8a" font-size="8">Quality features → stronger predictions</text>
        </svg>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Card 6: Model Evaluation -->
    <div class="concept-card fade-in">
      <div class="concept-icon">📊</div>
      <h3>Model Evaluation</h3>
      <p>Beyond accuracy: precision, recall, F1-score, and ROC-AUC reveal how well a model performs across classes. The confusion matrix shows exactly where predictions succeed or fail.</p>
      <div class="concept-diagram">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 340 160" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" style="background:rgba(0,0,0,0.3);border-radius:8px;">
          <!-- Confusion Matrix (left half) -->
          <text x="90" y="22" text-anchor="middle" fill="#52b788" font-size="9" font-weight="bold">Confusion Matrix</text>
          <!-- Header labels -->
          <text x="115" y="38" text-anchor="middle" fill="#7a9e8a" font-size="8">Pred +</text>
          <text x="155" y="38" text-anchor="middle" fill="#7a9e8a" font-size="8">Pred −</text>
          <text x="68" y="58" text-anchor="end" fill="#7a9e8a" font-size="8">Act +</text>
          <text x="68" y="88" text-anchor="end" fill="#7a9e8a" font-size="8">Act −</text>
          <!-- TP -->
