<section id="roadmap" style="background:rgba(45,106,79,0.05);border-top:1px solid var(--border);border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);padding:80px 2rem;">
  <div style="max-width:1100px;margin:0 auto;">
    <div class="section-header">
      <div class="section-tag">Your Journey</div>
      <h2>ML Learning Roadmap</h2>
      <p>Six stages from zero to production-ready ML engineer.</p>
    </div>
    <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fill,minmax(300px,1fr));gap:24px;">

      <div class="roadmap-card fade-in" style="background:var(--card-bg);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:var(--radius);padding:28px;position:relative;overflow:hidden;">
        <div style="position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:4px;height:100%;background:linear-gradient(180deg,#2d6a4f,#52b788);border-radius:4px 0 0 4px;"></div>
        <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;margin-bottom:16px;">
          <div style="width:36px;height:36px;border-radius:50%;background:rgba(45,106,79,0.4);border:2px solid #2d6a4f;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-weight:700;color:#52b788;font-size:0.9rem;">1</div>
          <h4 style="color:var(--green-light);font-size:1rem;">Math Foundations</h4>
        </div>
        <p style="font-size:0.85rem;color:var(--text-muted);margin-bottom:14px;">Linear algebra (vectors, matrices, dot products), calculus (derivatives, chain rule), probability &amp; statistics (distributions, Bayes).</p>
